# Tailwind

- Use Tailwind CSS v4 for styling; avoid vanilla CSS in `<style>` blocks
- Do **not** use `space-y-*` or `space-x-*`; use flex or grid with `gap-*` instead
- Tailwind uses `@tailwindcss/postcss`; global styles go in `app/globals.css`
